natural boundary
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a cliff, gully, river, gorge or thick bush separating two properties or areas [ possibly retaining stock without fencing. ]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
